@startuml UC_ViewOrderHistory_Sequence
title View Order History

actor "Customer" as User

participant "Web Client" as WebClient
participant "Orders API" as OrdersAPI

User -> WebClient: open order history page
WebClient -> OrdersAPI: fetch order history
OrdersAPI --> WebClient: list of orders
WebClient --> User: show order list

User -> WebClient: select order
WebClient -> OrdersAPI: fetch order detail
OrdersAPI --> WebClient: order detail
WebClient --> User: show order detail

@enduml
